			<div class="content" id="post-content-2729908">
									

<p>This guide has been rewritten as part of the Grand Crosslinking. The original version of this page can be found in archive form <a href="/task-forces-arc-2">here</a>.</p>
<p>With this version, we standardize the method of featuring a particular MTF. The number of articles was waived in two cases: Alpha-1 (&quot;Red Right Hand&quot;), and, for the various SCP: CB fans, Epsilon-11 (&quot;Nine-Tailed Fox&quot;).</p>
<p>Many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirens" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2802387); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2802387&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="Sirens" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2802387)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirens" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2802387); return false;">Sirens</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span> of the WikiWalk team for their assistance throughout (especially design ideas and coding), <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1346995); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1346995&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="Crayne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1346995)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1346995); return false;">Crayne</a></span> for <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/ye-olde-list-of-mtfs" target="_blank">listing out</a> the articles for me to hunt everyone down quickly, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(732274); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=732274&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="thedeadlymoose" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=732274)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(732274); return false;">thedeadlymoose</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(451071); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=451071&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="TroyL" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=451071)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(451071); return false;">TroyL</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span> for oversight and approval.</p>
<p>Extra special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484863282" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span> for all the incredible art. So much beautiful art.</p>

